tool_description: Are you a passionate music lover on the hunt for the ultimate festival experience? Look no further! Welcome to the Music Festival Hub, your comprehensive source of information for all things related to music festivals. Whether you're a seasoned festival-goer or a first-timer, this article aims to provide you with everything you need to know to make the most of your festival adventure.

api_list.name: Add to Order
Create Product
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://demo-project35830.p.rapidapi.com/catalog/product"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "demo-project35830.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
